  "body": "### Version Information\r\n\r\n* vyper Version (output of `vyper --version`): 0.3.3\r\n* OS: macOS\r\n* Python Version (output of `python --version`): 2.7.16\r\n\r\n### What's your issue about?\r\n\r\n#### Source codes:\r\n\r\nA.vy:\r\n```\r\n@external\r\n@payable\r\ndef __default__():\r\n    raise \"no_receive\"\r\n\r\n```\r\nC.vy:\r\n```\r\nimport A as A\r\n\r\na: A\r\n\r\n@external\r\ndef __init__(_a: address):\r\n    self.a = A(create_forwarder_to(_a))\r\n\r\n@external\r\n@payable\r\ndef __default__():\r\n    pass\r\n\r\n@external\r\ndef f():\r\n    send(self.a.address, as_wei_value(1, \"wei\"))\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### Problem\r\n\r\nIf set balance of contract C to 10 wei(for example) and call f(), it will return an exception with empty return data (But fallback in contract A reverts with string).",
